					<p class="text-secondary-400 text-center mb-12">Last updated: January 2025</p>

					<div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">
						<div class="card-base p-8 clip-lg">
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-white uppercase mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
							<p class="text-secondary-300 leading-relaxed">
								By accessing and using the RoweTech Machine & Engineering website and services, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our website or services.
							</p>
						</div>

