							<h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-white uppercase mb-4">2. Services</h2>
							<p class="text-secondary-300 leading-relaxed">
								RoweTech Machine & Engineering provides precision machining, mold repair, custom fixtures, EOAT tooling, and related manufacturing services. All quotes, orders, and services are subject to our standard terms and conditions, which will be provided upon request.
							</p>
						</div>

						<div class="card-base p-8 clip-lg">
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-white uppercase mb-4">3. Quote Requests</h2>
							<p class="text-secondary-300 leading-relaxed">
								Information submitted through our contact form is used solely for the purpose of responding to your inquiry and providing quotes for our services. Quotes are valid for 30 days unless otherwise specified and are subject to final review upon receipt of complete specifications.
							</p>
						</div>

						<div class="card-base p-8 clip-lg">
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-white uppercase mb-4">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
							<p class="text-secondary-300 leading-relaxed">
